{
  "texts": [
    "Coder The role of SQL Coder is to convert the agent-generated intent into SQL queries and return the results retrieved from the database.",
    "In the implementation, the SQL Coder and the agent share the same model.",
    "Since the model's conversion to SQL syntax is not always successful, the SQL Coder can make up to three attempts based on the error messages encountered.",
    "Spacy SpaCy is used to extract all medicalspecific terms from the input paragraph.",
    "To enhance the efficiency of entity extraction, we employ the en_core_sci_sm foot_15 model from SciSpaCy foot_16 as the NER model."
  ]
}